dialogue.subtitleText: A little shaky, but vertical take-offs take some practice.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000016 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Let's head back. Guess you need more time in the sims.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000016 244f4450-b06d-475d-a5aa-92b960945259
dialogue.subtitleText: Yeah, I don't think your ship can take any more. I think we'll need to get it patched up and try again.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000018 94c4cbc9-eba3-4c0e-9720-ca892bb2f3b0
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to Abernathy Interiors. How may I help you?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: What do you have for sale?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000018 94c4cbc9-eba3-4c0e-9720-ca892bb2f3b0
dialogue.subtitleText: Only the best furniture at the lowest price. Feel free to browse our showroom as you wish.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I have some stuff for sell.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000019 fea2c837-2e78-4641-b97b-51e429f93083
dialogue.subtitleText:
Welcome to the Advocacy Office, citizien.
Do you have something to report?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I want to report a crime.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000019 fea2c837-2e78-4641-b97b-51e429f93083
dialogue.subtitleText: What crime would you like to report?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I want to pay my bounty.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000019 fea2c837-2e78-4641-b97b-51e429f93083
dialogue.subtitleText: Please fill out this crime report.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000019 fea2c837-2e78-4641-b97b-51e429f93083
dialogue.subtitleText: Please fill out this crime report.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001A 435fc1f5-864a-4f03-b1cb-69ce4b7b7d08
dialogue.subtitleText:
If you have something to report,
please see the officer at the main desk.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001B e554a64d-2969-462c-8dc6-ff57f00c90e3
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to ArcCorp Bar! What can I serve you?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001B e554a64d-2969-462c-8dc6-ff57f00c90e3
dialogue.subtitleText: We have everything from pure water to the highest-quality space alcool.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: Any big news I might have missed?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001B e554a64d-2969-462c-8dc6-ff57f00c90e3
dialogue.subtitleText: I don't think so. Things have been pretty quiet lately.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001B e554a64d-2969-462c-8dc6-ff57f00c90e3
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm always there if you change your mind.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002C c5b05b9f-0641-4b97-9672-489018caafd8
dialogue.subtitleText:
I used to be in the army.
I was a Hornet pilot, fighting the Vanduul in Tiber.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002C c5b05b9f-0641-4b97-9672-489018caafd8
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm sure I could teach you a thing or two about dogfighting.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText:
I served in the Navy too, fighting the Vanduul.
I guess war never changes.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002C c5b05b9f-0641-4b97-9672-489018caafd8
dialogue.subtitleText:
Well, one day you're risking your life protecting all of mankind,
the next you're alone drinking in a lousy bar in the middle of nowhere!

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002C c5b05b9f-0641-4b97-9672-489018caafd8
dialogue.subtitleText: Alright, come back later and we'll have a drink.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001C ec4bd416-b9f6-4eaa-88ae-6cf02025cda8
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to ArcCorp Bar! What can I serve you?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001C ec4bd416-b9f6-4eaa-88ae-6cf02025cda8
dialogue.subtitleText: We have everything from pure water to the highest-quality space alcohol.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001C ec4bd416-b9f6-4eaa-88ae-6cf02025cda8
dialogue.subtitleText: Just give me a sign if you need anything.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001D 52ac6ea3-e9ee-4ad0-ba3d-dacd1d2f1589
dialogue.subtitleText:
Welcome to ArcCorp Distro and Job Well.
How may I be of service?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001D 52ac6ea3-e9ee-4ad0-ba3d-dacd1d2f1589
dialogue.subtitleText:
ArcCorp is always looking for raw materials to use in its factories.
We have lots of industrial good for sale.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001D 52ac6ea3-e9ee-4ad0-ba3d-dacd1d2f1589
dialogue.subtitleText: Anything else I can help you with?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001D 52ac6ea3-e9ee-4ad0-ba3d-dacd1d2f1589
dialogue.subtitleText: We have a few contracts available. Please have a look at the board.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001E 881a3cd3-a8d2-47f5-bfb7-9ada3016e83d
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to ArcCorp Store. We have all the latest technologies from ArcCorp available at the lowest price.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'd like to see what you have for sale.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001E 881a3cd3-a8d2-47f5-bfb7-9ada3016e83d
dialogue.subtitleText: Sure thing. Let me show you our newest fusion engine. It's a true marvel of engineering.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001E 881a3cd3-a8d2-47f5-bfb7-9ada3016e83d
dialogue.subtitleText: We'll give you the best price for your original ArcCorp parts.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001F 161f62d9-aca2-4f96-bac6-a660ec438824
dialogue.subtitleText: Hi! What can I do for you?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'd like to know about your insurance packages.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000001F 161f62d9-aca2-4f96-bac6-a660ec438824
dialogue.subtitleText:
I'm sure we have the perfect package to suit your needs.
It all depends on the level of coverage you want.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000020 89f5506e-f4a8-41d2-a85c-4d25d5962c13
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to Astro-Armada! How can I help you today?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'd like to sell my ship.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000020 89f5506e-f4a8-41d2-a85c-4d25d5962c13
dialogue.subtitleText:
You've come to the right place.
We'll give you the most credits for you ship.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'd like to buy a ship.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000020 89f5506e-f4a8-41d2-a85c-4d25d5962c13
dialogue.subtitleText: We have our most popular model right here on the show floor, and many more in our hangar.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000020 89f5506e-f4a8-41d2-a85c-4d25d5962c13
dialogue.subtitleText: Let me know if you have any questions.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'd like to get insurance for my ship.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000020 89f5506e-f4a8-41d2-a85c-4d25d5962c13
dialogue.subtitleText: Let me check with our insurance representative. He should be with you in just a minute.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000020 89f5506e-f4a8-41d2-a85c-4d25d5962c13
dialogue.subtitleText: Our insurance representative is ready. You can meet him in his office.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000021 2a5af666-4f6b-4919-bdc2-19fdcd70abfb
dialogue.subtitleText: How may I help you today?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I want to write my will.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000021 2a5af666-4f6b-4919-bdc2-19fdcd70abfb
dialogue.subtitleText: Sure. We have this easy form you can fill out.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000021 2a5af666-4f6b-4919-bdc2-19fdcd70abfb
dialogue.subtitleText: Anything else I can help you with?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm here to collect my inheritance.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000021 2a5af666-4f6b-4919-bdc2-19fdcd70abfb
dialogue.subtitleText: We are sorry for your loss, but we'll do our best to make this process easy for you.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm sorry, I changed my mind.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000022 2c9d9ec0-ff46-4349-826f-7d0ab9a049ef
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to Barclay's Estate. How may we help?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'd like to talk with a lawyer please.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000022 2c9d9ec0-ff46-4349-826f-7d0ab9a049ef
dialogue.subtitleText: One of our qualified lawyers will be available in just a minute, please have a seat.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000022 2c9d9ec0-ff46-4349-826f-7d0ab9a049ef
dialogue.subtitleText: Our lawyer is ready to meet with you. Please go through this door, his office is the first on the right.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm sorry, I have to go

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000022 2c9d9ec0-ff46-4349-826f-7d0ab9a049ef
dialogue.subtitleText: Don't forget, Barclay's Estate is always there for you.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000023 2425d98d-a920-4966-829b-662c7595123f
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to Casaba Outlet. How may I help you?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000023 2425d98d-a920-4966-829b-662c7595123f
dialogue.subtitleText: We have a great selection of clothes for every occasion.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'd like to try out these clothes.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000023 2425d98d-a920-4966-829b-662c7595123f
dialogue.subtitleText: Sure. Just go into any of the unoccupied changing room.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000023 2425d98d-a920-4966-829b-662c7595123f
dialogue.subtitleText: Come see me if you need to try anything.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000024 2502ef4e-2268-40af-952b-9c10642567db
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to Centermass. How may I be of service?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: What do you have for sale?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000024 2502ef4e-2268-40af-952b-9c10642567db
dialogue.subtitleText: We have the latest weapons and defensive countermeasures from ASD, Klaus & Werner, MaxOx, and many others.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000024 2502ef4e-2268-40af-952b-9c10642567db
dialogue.subtitleText: Can I help you in some other way?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I have some parts I'd like to sell.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000024 2502ef4e-2268-40af-952b-9c10642567db
dialogue.subtitleText: We're always looking for quality parts.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000024 2502ef4e-2268-40af-952b-9c10642567db
dialogue.subtitleText: Remember, when you fire, you can't go wrong with Centermass.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000028 82cb06da-caf4-4f3d-850c-133c88dab60e
dialogue.subtitleText:
BlackJack Securities is keeping ArcCorp safe.
Don't start any trouble.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002D 8ebf6221-bb16-4283-9a6c-3345b3c7012a
dialogue.subtitleText:
You look like you can defend yourself.
Are you looking for work?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I can always use some extra credits.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002D 8ebf6221-bb16-4283-9a6c-3345b3c7012a
dialogue.subtitleText:
I have some important work to get done,
but you need to keep a low profile.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002D 8ebf6221-bb16-4283-9a6c-3345b3c7012a
dialogue.subtitleText: I don't want any unwanted attention. Are you up for it?

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002D 8ebf6221-bb16-4283-9a6c-3345b3c7012a
dialogue.subtitleText: I might have misjudged you then.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'm just the man for the task.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002D 8ebf6221-bb16-4283-9a6c-3345b3c7012a
dialogue.subtitleText: Alright. I'll contact you when everything is ready.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: This isn't the kind of work I'm looking for.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002D 8ebf6221-bb16-4283-9a6c-3345b3c7012a
dialogue.subtitleText:
Let me know if you change your mind.
There's good money to be made for both of us

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000027 f33d0e07-5b41-4a5a-ae0a-4d83284ffba7
dialogue.subtitleText: Welcome to Cubby Blast. I'm Clor Vee, offering you the best in personal weapons in this part of the galaxy.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000027 f33d0e07-5b41-4a5a-ae0a-4d83284ffba7
dialogue.subtitleText:
I only stock the finest weapons and I test them all myself.
That's Cubby Blast's commitment to quality.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I have some weapons to sell

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000027 f33d0e07-5b41-4a5a-ae0a-4d83284ffba7
dialogue.subtitleText: Let me see what you have and I'll give you a price.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I'd like to buy parts for my ship.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002A 28625597-0750-48cc-aa65-f22bce26c92d
dialogue.subtitleText:
Good, cause that's all we're selling.
Everything we have is on the shelves behind you.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000017 6599f4fb-de56-475c-824c-f52cb9ee0512
dialogue.subtitleText: I have some extra parts I'd like to sell.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002A 28625597-0750-48cc-aa65-f22bce26c92d
dialogue.subtitleText: Alright, I can always take a look at what you have and give you a price.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002B c20870dd-f589-49d0-b896-6e7133ab3131
dialogue.subtitleText:
I'm pretty busy right now.
Go see the manager at the counter.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000031 aabc84cf-a6d4-4131-b7f9-d344da5bed8c
dialogue.subtitleText:
Legendary Fighter Pilot Area Riley once said Give me a fully loaded Hornet, and I ll shake the gates of Heaven.
Anvil Aerospaces Hornets have faced Vanduul, Shion, Pirates and Criminals.
Anvil Aerospaces Hornets have logged more combat time and kills in more theatres than any other ship in the history of Space Combat.
Battle Tested in the harshest conditions, the Hornet has proven time and again its ability to withstand damage, and still be able to dish it out.
With all the punishment it handles on a daily basis, don=t you think the new Hornet can handle yours
Anvil s New Hornet F7C, see your authorized ship dealer for options.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:0000002F 59ec243f-3512-49df-a9f5-bc0da1454268
dialogue.subtitleText:
We are drawn towards the familiar. It is safe, reliable.
But it can shackle us to the ordinary when in our souls we long to strike out and become something new.
We started with a simple match. Dare to dream. Dare to challenge the expectations of what has come before.
To embrace the Unique, to put everything on the line.
Only when we risk everything can we discover something truly special, and redefine what it means to drive with the stars.
To explore the farthest reaches, to race on the cutting edge, to Protect what you love.
Say goodbye to the familiar, and welcome the brand new Mustang, where risk, meets reward.

dialogue.speaker: varReference:00000030 33cb9aa3-418c-48d8-b887-c3803b44df72
dialogue.subtitleText:
Space, the best ships gracefully dance across its expense, the worst clumsily plod across its face. The new M50 doesnt have time for any of that.
Instead, it simply slices its way through.The 2944 M50 was designed with one goal in mind: Make the ship that will win the next Murray Cup.
The surprising thing is, Origin may have just about done it.
The stats are an orgy of mind-bending numbers but it comes down to two things. Less weight and more power. Youll notice the nose cone has grown what I can only describe as a mustache, added to stabilize all the additional thrust that the retooled and updated Twin Hammer HM4point3 drives spew out. And the refinement doesnt stop there.
They ve narrowed the front fuselage, moved the wings forward for better balance, shaved the cockpit viewpane down to the finest it could still be and not shatter in your face.
The result. A pure flying machine. Each movement on the stick translates directly into unadulterated throttle action. Welcome back to the glory days of flying.
